            </m:semantics>
          </m:math>
        </equation>
        <para id="id1164722507182">Question: An electronic signal is passed through an amplifier. Suppose that the power present in the signal at the input to the amplifier is 10 W. The power present in the signal at the output of the amplifier is 20 W. Express the gain of the amplifier in decibels.</para>
        <para id="id1164730577476">We can use equation (2) to easily express the gain of the amplifier in terms of decibels </para>
        <equation id="id1164722433030">
          <m:math>
            <m:semantics>
              <m:mrow>
